&gt; I&#39;d just like to add that the serial numbered swords are limited to
&gt; the NCO shin guntos with aluminium cast handle. I have seen many other
&gt; so-called Japanese swords with serial numbers on the blade, and these
&gt; were almost all Chinese fakes. For some reason, they think this
&gt; increases the value or legitimacy.
&gt; After the war, most of the civilian swords (bar a few identified as
&gt; art objects) were confiscated, not registered.
&gt; There is very little chance of tracking down the original owners or
&gt; history of 99% of these swords.
